prompts:
Create the complete Playwright E2E test suite for Z.ai integration:

1. Create .env.test file in /Users/sem/mao-Z/ with test ports (9503 backend, 5275 frontend)
2. Create all test files in /Users/sem/mao-Z/__tests__/e2e/
3. Include comprehensive test coverage for agent creation, tools, hooks, and provider switching
4. Create README.md with setup and run instructions
5. After creating files, run sync_env.sh to copy .env.test to backend and frontend

IMPORTANT: Use test ports 9503/5275 to avoid conflicts with production MAO instance running on 9403/5175.

Document everything clearly so tests can be run repeatedly.
